description:
In this festive karaoke version of Hark! The Herald Angels Sing, the angels sing of joy and hope for the future. Join in on the fun and sing along to this classic Christmas song!

Motion Graphics Used : Sis.Surangani Rosi - NAMADUMA https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKJhoXuYEfnpHXLEIuH5CIw/videos
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Karaoke
